{"tid":140402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[反了]中國史劇「奸人冊」  習近平等中共高層冊上有名","createTime":"2017-03-02T07:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T12:35:51.000Z","uid":53698,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d585e3d97cfdc01a854bc4b7a4db8b67d297ec92","tid":140402,"uid":53698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ny43302.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fny43302.jpg&h=e3239592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【中國史劇現「奸臣冊」　習近平等中共高層冊上有名】<br />\n中國歷史劇《大秦帝國之崛起》一幕出現「趙國奸細」名冊，習近平等中國共產黨高層均有出現於名冊之上，中國網友發現後，第30集隨即於各大網站上下架，中國網絡搜尋器亦無法搜尋大秦帝國之崛起。其後中國各大網站重新上載的30集已經沒有名冊近鏡一幕。<br />\n中國央視於2月28日黃金時段播放的歷史劇《大秦帝國之崛起》，其中一幕講述長平之戰，秦國人搜集趙國的奸細名單，想收買這群奸細。劇中演員打開奸細名單，畫面就出現了名單特寫，以小篆字體書寫，從右至左可見為胡錦濤、溫家寶、習近平、李克強、賈慶林。據悉中國網友稱呼共產黨高層為「趙家人」，即等同直接暗示這些趙家人是奸臣。而導演丁黑的名字亦有出現在奸細名冊的左半邊，相信是自嘲。"},{"pid":"c1eaaf591d76dcf5cd0d283bf1822b16f2232fa4","tid":140402,"uid":53698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:13:40.000Z","msg":"原文<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/03-01-2017/36249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F03-01-2017%2F36249&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=1f70d5a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/03-01-2017/36249</a>"},{"pid":"b76a06e21ab67541d5c46af1fafeaaf90018bbf4","tid":140402,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:14:59.000Z","msg":"導演rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ade34497e1effc78938f9fcb7a9cda873ee0d7a","tid":140402,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:15:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>導演rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbtw 關我鳩事"},{"pid":"73b2e87feb3007d634a9d8ce8d451285d02e6e8c","tid":140402,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl